latestPosts.caption:
SAWASDEE KA 🇹🇭🙏🏼If you’re looking to explore authentic Thai food and drinks from different regions of Thailand, don’t miss @thaifestivalchicago Not only will you get to taste incredible Thai cuisine, but you’ll also experience the richness of Thai culture—all in one place.

Join us on the grounds of Thorek Hospital, June 14–15—mark your calendars! This annual celebration is a must for food lovers, culture enthusiasts, and families looking for a unique Chicago summer experience.

#ThaiFestivalChicago #ThaiFestivalChicago2025 #thingstodoinchicago #thaifoodinchicago #chicagoland #chicagofoodauthority
